Quantum Considers Increasing Methanol Production

Quantum Chemical Corp. (99 Park Ave., New York, NY 10016; Tel
212/949-5000) has taken its LaPorte, TX methanol plant off the
market.  The unit, which has a capacity of 200 million
gallons/year, is operating at only 100 million gallons/year due
