move is unrelated to its pending acquisition by Hanson PLC (1
Grosvenor Pl., London SW1X 7JH, England).  The company is studying
options to increase the output of the plant to respond to a
perceived increase in demand for methanol stemming from oxygenated
gasoline requirements.




