Genetron AZ-50, a mixture of hydrofluorocarbon (HFC)-125 and (HFC)-
143a, at its Baton Rouge, LA facility in June 1994.  Allied-Signal
has also received Underwriters Laboratories (UL) approval of the
product, certifying it for use with UL-approved equipment.
Genetron AZ-50 is a replacement for the refrigerant R-502, a
mixture of CFC-115 and HCFC-22.




